  "description": "The archetype. Taiko delivers a punishing four-on-the-floor kick column. Beatbox snare marks beats 2 and 4. Tight closed hi-hats run the 16th-note grid. Open hi-hat on the and-of-4 creates the driving upbeat push. GATHER is your build macro — sweep it up to stack the full ensemble before the drop.",
